snippet.title: [FULL] Love Dramatic - Kaguya-sama: Love is War OP - Piano Arrangement [Synthesia]
snippet.description:
Full version of the opening to Kaguya-sama: Love is War (Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Tensai-tachi no Renai Zunousen in Romaji, but that's ridiculously long and I couldn't fit it in the title), Love Dramatic!

I've been looping the full version ever since it came out, and man is it a good song. 

And for once, my arrangement has nothing really crazy in it! This is probably the easiest full version I have ever written!

Ok, there's three hand technique at 2:05, but hey each song need a challenge!
Oh and also at 2:23 it's not a really fast run it's a black keys glissando so it's not as hard as it looks. Don't worry.

Hope you enjoy the simple(-ish?) arrangement of the best OP of this season! (debatable)
